<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4693513>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 56–61. Palpada chilena (Rondani, 1863): (56) male visiting a Lantara camara L., Santiago (photo by Orlando Montes); (57) female resting in a leave, Pucón (Photo by Miguel Mellado). Palpada elegans (Blanchard, 1852): (58) female visiting a Trifolium sp., Santiago (photo by Matías Cortés); (59) male visiting an Asteraceae, Lago Lanalhue (photo by Edgardo Flores). Palpada meigenii (Wiedemann, 1830): (60) males visiting Foeniculum vulgare Mill., Biobío river (photo by Orlando Montes); (61) female resting, Puerto Montt (photo by Matías Cortés)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693513/files/figure.png" .

